Privacy Policy for Miners World

Last updated: [Current Date]

1. Information We Collect
- Wallet addresses
- Game activity data
- Device information

2. How We Use Information
- To provide and maintain the game service
- To process in-game transactions
- To improve user experience
- To communicate with users

3. Information Storage
- Game data is stored on the TON blockchain
- No personal information is stored on our servers
- We do not collect or store private keys

4. Information Sharing
We do not share or sell user information to third parties.

5. Security
We implement security measures to protect your information.

6. Changes to Privacy Policy
We may update this policy from time to time.

7. Contact
For privacy concerns, contact privacy@miners-world.com 